      • setConcertMasterFlag

        public void setConcertMasterFlag(Boolean concertMasterFlag)
        Sets the concert master flag based on the Boolean value given. If the value is true the user is proclaimed a concert master. If the value is false the user is proclaimed a second conert msater. If the value equals null the player does not have any special function in the section.
        Parameters:
        concertMasterFlag - - a Boolean object

      • getConcertMasterFlag

        public Boolean getConcertMasterFlag()
        Works as a inverse method to setConcertMasterFlag(java.lang.Boolean). Returns true if the player is concert master, false if the player is second concert master and null if the player does not have any function in his section.
        Returns:
        a Boolean object
